16 established by law and by the pay plan developed under section
17 27 of this chapter.
18 (2) As a factor in making promotions.
19 (3) As a means of discovering employees:
20 (A) who are candidates for promotion or transfer; or
21 (B) who, because of a low service rating, are candidates for
22 demotion or dismissal.
